      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and a screaming 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for pure mechanical engagement. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including rod bearing replacement and throttle valve actuators. The chassis retains factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise high-frequency damping. Finished in flawless Alpine White over Novillo leather, this is a superlative, high-revving icon for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
